	" is a fighting game for the C64 developed by Beam Software and published by Melbourne House in 1985. It has a unique mechanic in that the player needs to reach 2 points by punching or kicking their opponent before they do. When time runs out, the winner is determined by whoever has more points. The fights get progressively harder as the player progresses.
